snippet.title: Catroots [Nintendo 64 Unreleased Game - Alpha Tech Demo]
snippet.description:
http://www.unseen64.net

May 16, 2000 - Okay, we still don't know much more about this game then we did at E3, but we're going to present this highly prized movie footage that was on display at Nintendo's booth anyway. Comparisons to Itchy and Scratchy are sure to follow and if it's an N64 game on the way from NCL, then that's just fine with us.

We've ruled out the possibility that we're looking at a Dolphin game, because we assume the next generation machine will be able to crank out better graphics than this. It certainly looks like something the N64 could do and looks darn good by N64 standards at that.

As we told you in our previous story, Nintendo of America is in the dark about this game as well. 

http://ign64.ign.com/articles/079/079625p1.html
